What is Prometheus ?

It is a open-source monitoring tool which helps to collects the Metrics like CPU Usage, Memory, Nerworks etc


What is Loki ?

It is open-source logging tool which used to and save the logs of pods, Services, Metrics, Namespace from promtail



What is Promtail ?

It is open-source logging tool which used to and save the logs from Pods, Services, Metrics, Namespace


What is Grafana ?

It is a open-source monitoring tool which helps to visualize the data like prometheus data or logging data in the form of dashboard
